{
  "id": "api/core/ViewEncapsulation",
  "title": "ViewEncapsulation",
  "contents": "<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/ViewEncapsulation\", \"name\": \"ViewEncapsulation\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/metadata/view.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20请简述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/15.0.1/packages/core/src/metadata/view.ts\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"viewencapsulation\">ViewEncapsulation<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#viewencapsulation\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label enum\">enum</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p>Defines the CSS styles encapsulation policies for the <a href=\"api/core/Component\"><code>Component</code></a> decorator's\n<code>encapsulation</code> option.</p>\n<p>定义可用于 Component 的 <a href=\"api/core/Component\"><code>Component</code></a> 的模板和样式封装选项。</p>\n\n    <p no-translate=\"\"><a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#description\">查看\"说明\"...</a></p>\n  </section>\n<section class=\"enum-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\nenum <a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewEncapsulation</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#Emulated\"><span class=\"member-name\">Emulated</span>: 0</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#None\"><span class=\"member-name\">None</span>: 2</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#ShadowDom\"><span class=\"member-name\">ShadowDom</span>: 3</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n</section>\n\n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p>See <a href=\"api/core/Component#encapsulation\">encapsulation</a>.</p>\n<p>请参阅 <a href=\"api/core/Component#encapsulation\">encapsulation</a>。</p>\n  <p>Further information is available in the <a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#usage-notes\">Usage Notes...</a></p>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"members\">\n  <a name=\"properties\"></a>\n  <h2 id=\"members\">成员列表<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#members\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>成员</th>\n        <th>说明</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr class=\"member\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"Emulated\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">Emulated</span>: 0</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <div no-translate=\"\"><p>Emulates a native Shadow DOM encapsulation behavior by adding a specific attribute to the\ncomponent's host element and applying the same attribute to all the CSS selectors provided\nvia <a href=\"api/core/Component#styles\">styles</a> or <a href=\"api/core/Component#styleUrls\">styleUrls</a>.</p>\n<p>通过向宿主元素添加包含替代 ID 的属性并预处理通过 <a href=\"api/core/Component#styles\">styles</a> 或 <a href=\"api/core/Component#styleUrls\">styleUrls</a> 提供的样式规则，来模拟 <code>Native</code> 所有选择器。</p></div>\n          <p>This is the default option.</p>\n<p>这是默认选项。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"member\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"None\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">None</span>: 2</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <div no-translate=\"\"><p>Doesn't provide any sort of CSS style encapsulation, meaning that all the styles provided\nvia <a href=\"api/core/Component#styles\">styles</a> or <a href=\"api/core/Component#styleUrls\">styleUrls</a> are applicable\nto any HTML element of the application regardless of their host Component.</p>\n<p>不要提供任何模板或样式封装。</p></div>\n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"member\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"ShadowDom\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">ShadowDom</span>: 3</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <div no-translate=\"\"><p>Uses the browser's native Shadow DOM API to encapsulate CSS styles, meaning that it creates\na ShadowRoot for the component's host element which is then used to encapsulate\nall the Component's styling.</p>\n<p>使用浏览器的本机 Shadow DOM API 来封装 CSS 样式，这意味着它会为组件的宿主元素创建一个\nShadowRoot，然后用该元素来封装所有组件的样式。</p></div>\n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <h3 id=\"example\">Example<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#example\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<h3 id=\"例子\">例子<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#例子\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<code-example path=\"core/ts/metadata/encapsulation.ts\" region=\"longform\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'app-root',\n  template: `\n    &#x3C;h1>Hello World!&#x3C;/h1>\n    &#x3C;span class=\"red\">Shadow DOM Rocks!&#x3C;/span>\n  `,\n  styles: [`\n    :host {\n      display: block;\n      border: 1px solid black;\n    }\n    h1 {\n      color: blue;\n    }\n    .red {\n      background-color: red;\n    }\n\n  `],\n  encapsulation: <a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#ShadowDom\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewEncapsulation.ShadowDom</a>\n})\nclass MyApp {\n}\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/APP_ID\n - api/core/CompilerOptions\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Renderer2\n - api/core/RendererType2\n - api/core/global/ComponentDebugMetadata\n - errors/NG2009\n - guide/complex-animation-sequences\n - guide/view-encapsulation\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Component#encapsulation\n - api/core/Component#styleUrls\n - api/core/Component#styles\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#Emulated\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#None\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#ShadowDom\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#description\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#example\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#members\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#usage-notes\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#viewencapsulation\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#例子\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/metadata/view.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20请简述你的修改...\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/15.0.1/packages/core/src/metadata/view.ts\n-->"
}